1. Every source file must begin with the header as follows. Add revision info
   everytime you modify the file.

   每个源文件必须以如下格式的文件头开始。每次修改文件均要添加修订信息。

/******************************************************************************/
/*  Unit Name:  RegisterFile                                                  */
/*  Created by: Kathy                                                         */
/*  Created on: 04/06/2018                                                    */
/*  Edited by:  Kathy                                                         */
/*  Edited on:  04/12/2018                                                    */
/*                                                                            */
/*  Description:                                                              */
/*      Register file with zero register.                                     */
/*      Note: Zero Register will reads zero, and write to Zero Register will  */
/*            be safely ignored.                                              */
/*                                                                            */
/*  Revisions:                                                                */
/*      04/06/2018  Kathy       Unit created.                                 */
/*      04/07/2018  Kathy       Add addr reg reset.                           */
/*      04/12/2018  Kathy       1) Remove reset signal and functionality.     */
/*                              2) Remove read addr reg, register read data.  */
/******************************************************************************/

2. Constant identifiers (including `define macros, parameters and localparams)
   contain only capital letters and underscores.

   常数标识符（包括`define宏、parameter参数和localparam参数）只包含大写字母和下划线。

3. Variable identifiers (including signals, module names, ports, instance names,
   function names and task names) contain only letters, numbers and underscores.
   Each word in an identifier begins with a capital letter and the remaining are
   small letters, with no intervening characters. All letters of abbreviation in
   an identifier are capital. Underscores are used to make it clear when there
   are successive capital letters except for abbreviation. (It's called CamelCase)

   变量标识符（包括信号名、模块名、端口名、实例名、函数名和任务名）只包含字母、数字和下划线。
   标识符中的每个单词以大写字母开头，其余字母小写，单词间没有分隔符。标识符中的缩写词全部
   使用大写字母。下划线用于分隔连续的大写字母使得标识符看起来清晰，缩写词中的大写字母不用
   下划线分隔。（这称为“骆驼风格”）

4. Comments write in English for the sake of compatibility with various tools.
   Comments can either be above or after the statement in the same line, and must
   not be under the statement.

   使用英文写注释，以便与各种工具保持兼容。注释可以在语句上面或同一行的后面，不允许写在
   语句下面。